    <detaileddescription>
<para>The note-arduino Arduino library for communicating with the <ulink url="https://blues.io">Blues Wireless</ulink> <ref refid="class_notecard" kindref="compound">Notecard</ref> via serial or I2C.</para>
<para>This library allows you to control a <ref refid="class_notecard" kindref="compound">Notecard</ref> by writing an Arduino sketch in C or C++. Your sketch may programmatically configure <ref refid="class_notecard" kindref="compound">Notecard</ref> and send Notes to <ulink url="https://notehub.io">Notehub.io</ulink>.</para>
<para>This library is a wrapper around the <ulink url="https://github.com/blues/note-c">note-c library</ulink>, which it includes as a git submodule.</para>
<para>Written by Ray Ozzie and Brandon Satrom for Blues Inc.</para>
